OL,3,CLabour's pledge not to raise working
OL,4,Cpeople's taxes 'not credible', IFS says
OL,6,FReform's claim they could eliminate
OL,7,FNHS waiting lists at a cost of #17
OL,8,Fbillion a year is "demonstrably wrong"
OL,9,Fand the #90 billion of promised tax
OL,10,Fcuts have echoes of Liz Truss in the
OL,11,Fsense there is "no detail on how they
OL,12,Fwould be paid for".
OL,14,FAs for the Greens, the plan for a
OL,15,Fcarbon tax-raising #90 billion a year
OL,16,Fwould reduce emissions but would also
OL,17,Fcause inflation and be "economically
OL,18,Fdisruptive".
