OL,6,FAs for spending cuts - where?
OL,8,FAs the IFS points out, unprotected
OL,9,Fgovernment departments - which fund
OL,10,Fjob centres, courts, and prisons and
OL,11,Fprovide subsidies for bus and train
OL,12,Fservices - have already seen their
OL,13,Fbudgets slashed in real terms in the
OL,14,Flast 14 years.
OL,16,FThe services they provide are under
OL,17,Fstrain.
