OL,4,Cpeople's taxes 'not credible', IFS says
OL,6,FAs for borrowing, the UK's stock of
OL,7,Fnational debt has risen to the highest
OL,8,Flevel in almost 70 years. And interest
OL,9,Fpayments doubled in the last
OL,10,Fparliament. The government now spends
OL,11,Faround #100 billion a year just
OL,12,Fservicing debt.
OL,14,FLow growth and high debt interest
OL,15,Fpayments are a serious problem and
OL,16,Fwill leave the next government boxed
OL,17,Fin.
