OL,3,CLabour's pledge not to raise working
OL,4,Cpeople's taxes 'not credible', IFS says
OL,6,FLabour's manifesto is a series of
OL,7,Fpolicies aimed at raising growth which
OL,8,Fthe IFS judges to be sensible,
OL,9,Falthough it warns they will take time
OL,10,Fto have an impact and planning reform
OL,11,Fwill be "technically difficult and
OL,12,Fpolitically painful".
OL,14,FBoth parties are telling you lots
OL,15,Fabout what they won't do if they form
OL,16,Fthe next government and not enough
OL,17,Fabout what they will do - particularly
OL,18,Fif the economic growth they are
OL,19,Fbetting on doesn't materialise.
